In [32]:
## Mean Absolute Percentage - Function Definition

def MAPE(y, yhat): 
    y, yhat = np.array(y), np.array(yhat)
    try:
        mape =  round(np.sum(np.abs(yhat - y)) / np.sum(y) * 100,2)
    except:
        print("Observed values are empty")
        mape = np.nan
    return mape
